Package logic

Class BranchReports

java.lang.Object
logic.BranchReports
public class BranchReports extends Object
This class represents the reports associated with a specific branch, including income, quarterly, performance, and order reports. It also holds information about the available years and months for which reports can be generated.
Version:
5.0

      Parameters:
      branchID - The branch associated with these reports.
      incomeReport - The list of income reports available to the user.
      firstquarterReport - The list of first quarter reports available to the user.
      secondquarterReport - The list of second quarter reports available to the user.
      performanceReport - The list of performance reports available to the user.
      orderReport - The list of order reports available to the user.
      yearMonth - A map of available years and months for report generation.
